I '''Ralph H. Baer''' (mibait [[Marsu 8]],[[1922]]) metung yang [[Germany|Aleman]]-bait [[United States|America]] [[talaimbentu]], bantug karing kayang dakal a ambag keng [[pialung]] ampong [[video game industry]]. Inyang 2006, mirinan yang galal keng [[National Medal of Technology]] para keng pamanimbentu na keng [[Video game console|home console for video games]].


